<p local-id=3D"2359c652-a7b7-4704-a2fb-745cd72e4ea2"><a href=3D"https://tbi=
group.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/TSFMPU/pages/4053106704/API+documentation+-=
+Fusion+Pay#Example-files" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>Example files</strong><=
/a></p></li>
</ol>
<p class=3D"media-group"><img height=3D"250" style=3D"margin: 2px; border: =
1px solid #ddd; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: text-bottom;" src=
=3D"060fdcf6e5d293e7142d715358e1ebfbd23e435337878e38e0234fa20b74b5c8" width=
=3D"250"></p>
<p local-id=3D"c1bd38c2-a6e8-482e-bd36-f0bf6b132f56"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"e587547e-db37-46bf-9384-f0710b1b6239" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-GeneralInformation">General Infor=
mation</h2>
<p local-id=3D"32f37db3-0a51-4216-9dea-999a290cd3ea"></p>
<p local-id=3D"cbecbfb3-7435-47c4-8402-ed4f52442142">This document serves a=
s a guide for merchants to integrate with the TBI Bank loan application pla=
tform using the provided API. The platform can be accessed through the foll=
owing URLs:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8430a637-9e52-4a1e-84c6-3a056e977b6c">
<li local-id=3D"ee797e92-0e77-4572-aec6-1291e6f04781">
<p local-id=3D"f9a8f164-70a8-49f5-8af2-59eeeb120d46"><strong>Test Environme=
nt:</strong> <a class=3D"external-link" data-card-appearance=3D"inline" hre=
f=3D"https://bankly-uat.tbibank.bg/#/login" local-id=3D"d4118cb0-9b69-42f6-=
a012-c2fa320ca602" rel=3D"nofollow">https://bankly-uat.tbibank.bg/#/login</=
a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0377aad1-0a15-478e-b069-6499302d8f49">
<p local-id=3D"d7d94212-13ff-4984-a56f-ba7735ccb973"><strong>Production Env=
ironment:</strong> <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://bnkl.tbibank.=
bg/#/login" rel=3D"nofollow">https://bnkl.tbibank.bg/#/login</a></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3fd3e966-6d16-4482-9fe2-6d2149e059d7">Upon registering for a=
 partnership with TBI Bank, merchants will receive access to these platform=
s to track all incoming loan applications. This guide refers to the platfor=
m as the "Merchant Portal." Merchants will also be provided with a 'reselle=
r code' (a four-character code) and a 'reseller key' to identify the store =
or object when using the API methods.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"1897e139-ec45-4e8a-8a18-339b8176187f" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-BankProducts">Bank Products</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a38d71ba-20dc-40f0-861e-021332580338">TBI Bank offers variou=
s repayment schemes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f214169b-9a96-488a-88f3-67819597057a">
<li local-id=3D"a54b5a44-2317-4b2f-b1e8-57393a1c3657">
<p local-id=3D"b2433e11-6617-44bc-901a-e17f3879362a">Loan terms range from =
3 to 60 months.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c69a9ac1-bc11-4d4c-a6dc-a048a97501d8">
<p local-id=3D"f0a39b95-9945-410c-961c-f19659996cdc">Loan amounts range fro=
m 50 to 15,000 EUR .</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a85590c7-7078-4a46-9339-abdf7202881d">
<p local-id=3D"4e83f974-0f65-4641-be80-e89259fb708d">Options include standa=
rd loans and "Buy Now, Pay Later" schemes.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3227bf3b-05ae-495d-bf92-d60607c6597a">
<p local-id=3D"e9d63dbe-5a44-44d5-8e33-992a34611b4e">Terms and interest rat=
es are agreed upon with the Merchant Enabler (a TBI Bank employee responsib=
le for the merchant).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa864512-ea4b-4f88-a996-25579594ba67">
<p local-id=3D"fc000d42-5247-4c24-b133-a75a589d336c">Interest rates can var=
y based on the loan amount, with options for 0% rates and promotional schem=
es for specific periods. These terms are also arranged with the Merchant En=
abler.</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"80e0e5fe-0153-4f87-b574-323bae555946" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-IntegrationProcess">Integration Process</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4c55f65c-c085-475e-a0b6-9ff03e11161d">The integration proces=
s for sending loan applications is divided into two main parts:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"1c9423bc-70f6-4793-9839-a62061faad8a" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Part1:DisplayFinancingOptions">Part 1: Display Financing Option=
s</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d056f0b4-b777-49ae-aee1-dceeee683761">
<li local-id=3D"6fdc1b63-7a0e-463a-a28d-14f4ceb00e83">
<p local-id=3D"59cac852-27fb-4d89-a120-28509c878edd"><strong>Display Financ=
ing Button:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d9565253-76d9-47da-ae86-d86755caa33c">
<li local-id=3D"514d16c8-9abe-4764-8da2-1cf92038bb63">
<p local-id=3D"470033f6-3d0f-403d-9768-c7c1d06d28b5">Show a button on the p=
roduct page saying "Buy in installments starting from XX.XX per month" or "=
Buy in X installments for XX.XX / monthly."</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"411c2f0f-01d1-4ef4-a4ed-72ad7fe628de">
<p local-id=3D"3f7e157c-c407-41b0-a006-f438d8e78830">Use the <code>GetCalcu=
lations</code> API method to calculate the installment amount (XX.XX).</p><=
/li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b6fff91-29d2-48f8-a95d-8bd5cb1bac0d">
<p local-id=3D"1fb9307b-85aa-4b52-8db9-0577b81c484d"><strong>Show All Pay S=
chemes:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"41a4c1ca-176b-4986-b581-cd02106d89c2">
<li local-id=3D"b33d950f-f67e-40c4-a380-d50c9e87b4a8">
<p local-id=3D"a518d3ad-c174-4153-8f59-869fb9d304ec">Allow the customer to =
view all available pay schemes with different periods.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"36be2ca6-944d-40a3-9adf-2fae585abd8c">
<p local-id=3D"7eb261aa-0378-4974-a25c-258530bdad41">Display this informati=
on on both the product and checkout pages.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"789c0113-a747-4052-bf18-872969add0a1">
<p local-id=3D"cb09e424-d093-4772-beb3-89798a32d199">Ensure that the follow=
ing EU-compliant parameters are displayed: APR, NIR, Total Due Amount, Inst=
allment, and Period. These details are provided by the <code>GetCalculation=
s</code> method.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"a4bdc12e-8f13-4b71-b347-55ddd2bec4d5" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Part2:SubmitLoanApplication">Part 2: Submit Loan Application</h=
3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"1b16850a-7af1-4a2b-9e9c-3241038e449d">
<li local-id=3D"b9c40243-eb66-4628-92d3-2edaa687c86a">
<p local-id=3D"8d4393df-4e69-4cd1-89c0-954d79999fd3"><strong>Send Loan Appl=
ication:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"80a44c82-77b0-4f7c-afe2-fadaa58b3ae8">
<li local-id=3D"3c9647db-f7c2-4a02-9e3c-9f42458b3a12">
<p local-id=3D"1dd39f8f-e03e-4bd4-978f-ae9eec36640f">Use the <code>Register=
Application</code> API method to send client data (e.g., Full Name, Phone N=
umber, Address) and shopping cart items to the bank.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"90068bad-362c-4692-8297-d2f014bef44d">
<p local-id=3D"4fe5afe6-c4ad-4e00-be2c-3caa05692a77">The only mandatory fie=
lds are the items list and the order ID from the merchant's website.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"7ff3d2df-2467-49bf-ae58-08a96a21885f">
<p local-id=3D"a1ae7062-6e09-42e8-902c-e71aff03966d">The <code>RegisterAppl=
ication</code> method returns a URL where the customer completes the applic=
ation. This URL can be used to redirect the customer or display a pop-up on=
 the website.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1dea4564-02e2-4c65-a800-90e37e5173f1">
<p local-id=3D"8a012f07-2376-4836-88d4-8f2bd3822302">Preferably, send custo=
mer data in the API call to prefill the application form, enhancing custome=
r satisfaction.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"5ba8a391-1b6e-41d1-92ce-3f9660d31ab0" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Extra:UpdateApplicationStatus">Extra: Update Application Status=
</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"24a92b6c-475a-4282-b115-10aa21ed8664">
<li local-id=3D"552cc6a6-7a52-4405-9bc2-453564daa7f2">
<p local-id=3D"3b37858a-9bdd-4a35-b561-73321c300423"><strong>Check Applicat=
ion Status:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"29a37044-2b8d-42b7-adc7-5a11a8eacefb">
<li local-id=3D"c97a7a43-a5bf-498f-826f-936d1fa23e9c">
<p local-id=3D"861fe425-4577-4138-8a88-ffc2d617a0b9">Use the <code>GetAppli=
cationStatus</code> endpoint to retrieve the current status of an applicati=
on and track its status changes throughout the processing.</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"cf9a9369-3d47-46ba-869a-6d7a28dfe344">By following these ste=
ps, merchants can seamlessly integrate with the TBI Bank loan application p=
latform, offering flexible financing options to their customers and ensurin=
g a smooth application process.</p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<h3 local-id=3D"0813faea-08de-42e3-87fc-31b0b491f596" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-FusionPay-ChangesintheAPIIntegrationRelatedtotheIntroductionoft=
heEuro(EUR)">Fusion Pay - Changes in the API Integration Related to the Int=
roduction of the Euro (EUR)</h3>
<h3 local-id=3D"c743a238-d61b-4a19-a7c2-2c88d3351b38" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-FusionPayEURO"><a href=3D"https://tbigroup.atlassian.net/wiki/x=
/AoCtRwE" rel=3D"nofollow">Fusion Pay EURO </a></h3>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"4588215a-fa95-459e-80ce-d25875e7d7a3" style=3D"text-align: c=
enter;"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"b99289e2-035f-4f28-a5f6-75be8fb5cb74" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-ApplicationFlowOverview"><strong>=
Application Flow Overview</strong></h2>
<p local-id=3D"9bbe4333-36be-4a11-ad6c-ae2872f8491d" style=3D"text-align: c=
enter;"></p>
<p local-id=3D"93261c38-d418-4293-baef-b030868260bd">This section provides =
a high-level overview of how the loan application process works when you in=
tegrate with tbi bank through Fusion Pay.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d88fd564-1155-4bcb-be44-cd9cb325ef52">The diagram shows the =
key steps your customer goes through - from choosing an installment option =
on your website, to submitting the application, and finally receiving a dec=
ision from the bank.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1ba5271b-67cf-4ac3-bf9f-1a5d4f7cab84">This overview helps yo=
u to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"db9f7511-021c-41c9-9c8e-1951b9027aaa">
<li local-id=3D"63c97030-a731-47dd-9ec9-831930de1f4f">
<p local-id=3D"0e328ed9-7e4e-43d8-a2e5-c4c95705e11c">Understand the complet=
e loan application flow at a glance.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"43ab3d1b-373d-46e6-bc5c-bdeb370ec0d3">
<p local-id=3D"e6021e6c-3755-431b-bab9-608671d5d48c">See how your website, =
Fusion Pay, and tbi bank systems work together.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f6c6bd2-d61f-4bcf-a9c4-4cfb2caf4966">
<p local-id=3D"2017fdc9-3af8-4732-adc5-b0c3a2b2453c">Recognize where the in=
tegration points described later in this documentation apply.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"169979aa-994c-4969-8113-0670eb49c2b6">Refer to this diagram =
to get the =E2=80=9Cbig picture=E2=80=9D before moving on to the technical =
details and examples in the following sections.</p><span class=3D"confluenc=
e-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-siz=
e"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"BPMN.jpg" w=
idth=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"c51b227e19f653f73936e08382ce91b4c6b7c7=
6d1ffaa80697aea93b76124426" data-image-src=3D"https://tbigroup.atlassian.ne=
t/wiki/download/attachments/4053106704/BPMN.jpg?version=3D1&amp;modificatio=
nDate=3D1755853325968&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"200=
2" data-width=3D"8192" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-reso=
urce-id=3D"5216862220" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resou=
rce-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"BPMN.jpg" dat=
a-base-url=3D"https://tbigroup.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-con=
tent-type=3D"image/jpeg" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"4053106704" d=
ata-linked-resource-container-version=3D"34" data-media-id=3D"bf73055a-215f=
-45b5-b0af-2d56089aabf5" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"114"></span>
<h2 local-id=3D"ae51921d-cc0a-47d5-ad01-6897cec02087" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-Methods">Methods</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"6d5abfd9-decb-4873-acee-1184ab9bbb62" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-GetCalculations">GetCalculations<=
/h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"a8a2e2fa-5f1a-464a-97c7-ab70ee98cfa5" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-Overview">Overview</h4>
<p local-id=3D"77d78246-51a9-443a-b68e-cb4c6f3fb967">The <code>GetCalculati=
ons</code> API call provides a RESTful response with available repayment sc=
hemes for a specific merchant or store. It supports both GET and POST reque=
sts. The response includes all necessary parameters to display repayment sc=
hemes in compliance with EU requirements and to facilitate sending applicat=
ions to the bank processing platform.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e8f7352d-b5aa-4d91-8959-0f768b959f79">To optimize performanc=
e, it's recommended to update the parameters once per day, preferably after=
 the first scheme request of the new day or after 00:01 daily. A manual pul=
l update API call from the merchant backend is also advisable if different =
interest rate conditions are set up.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c7d06c6c-1158-4a69-907a-902a32ae98eb">However, if the API is=
 called for each calculation, the response remains efficient and easy to ha=
ndle.</p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<h4 local-id=3D"a549c96d-ca03-4dfb-b63f-8e7198cd119a" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-PRODEndpoint:<https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetCalculations>=
">PROD Endpoint: <code>&lt;https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetCalculations=
</code>&gt;</h4>
</div>
</div>
