<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<h3 local-id=3D"1465a543-c0f6-41f9-9d34-43556d1d62a6" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-ImportantNotice">Important Notice</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a66ed02a-f2b5-4cbd-b525-ca9cc0384099">The <code>GetCalculati=
ons</code> API can receive all parameters via a GET request and has no limi=
tations since it does not handle sensitive information. However, setting th=
e code and key via GET is not recommended. The preferred usage is via data =
form POST or text/JSON raw POST request from the backend.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"3bc0fc44-edc4-49b8-98c1-91ce109996ad" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-ExamplecURLCommands">Example cURL Commands</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"1871cf44-bd3d-4126-884b-11978e6283cb">
<li local-id=3D"e16cd44c-c4a1-4f70-b670-36e53df53cce">
<p local-id=3D"166c32ff-7481-4543-8af1-c9c14e8f8875"><strong>Form Data POST=
 Request</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">curl --=
location '&lt;https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetCalculations&gt;' \\
--form 'reseller_code=3D"TBI1"' \\
--form 'reseller_key=3D"EMPTY"'</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f05821c-5c49-4f01-9a5f-26025ca297a9">
<p local-id=3D"857877e8-3a3b-49b7-9db4-3be8eef05e39"><strong>JSON POST Requ=
est</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">curl --=
location '&lt;https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetCalculations&gt;' \\
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\
--data '{"reseller_code":"TBI1","reseller_key":"EX1","category_id":"255","a=
mount":"1000"}'</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li local-id=3D"80daa154-6bc8-4177-ac8e-70eb457df7f5">
<p local-id=3D"2f0f10ed-c1a3-4eff-a72e-13970386db25"><strong>Text/Plain POS=
T Request</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">curl --=
location '&lt;https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetCalculations&gt;' \\
--header 'Content-Type: text/plain' \\
--data '{"reseller_code":"TBI1","reseller_key":"EX1","category_id":"255","a=
mount":"1000"}'</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"2e649c47-a92b-4f17-8825-a30c459e19e5"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"7651550e-5c01-4c08-8c8c-62883bf26dc0" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-RegisterApplication">Register App=
lication</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"5f8ebd0b-98a4-40ef-8955-94ffd68eadcc" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-Overview.1">Overview</h3>
<p local-id=3D"093b36e7-2c72-4d6f-97d9-d5a601155077"></p>
<p local-id=3D"2ee5a5ff-15e5-4281-a515-b59164e7162f">The <code>RegisterAppl=
ication</code> method sends customer and order data to TBI Bank. If the dat=
a is valid, the response includes a URL to which the customer should be red=
irected to complete the application. This endpoint supports only the POST m=
ethod.</p>
<p local-id=3D"470ddfeb-e149-485d-b426-dd888ac5e13e">For testing, use the f=
ollowing credentials:</p>
<div class=3D"panel" style=3D"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998D=
D9;border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"panelContent" style=3D"background-color: #EAE6FF;">
<ul local-id=3D"ed0bacc3-7d82-48d0-a1ea-ba70df827b55">
<li local-id=3D"c9f5d32f-26f2-4e82-b80d-a6f680099210">
<p local-id=3D"e899ae85-ff34-4fd5-ace7-db0aad08dbb5"><strong>reseller_code:=
</strong> TBI1</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8705c044-d918-48de-949b-a04d01b79197">
<p local-id=3D"4550b11c-7a05-4613-9f69-56b6f594c167"><strong>reseller_key:<=
/strong> EX1</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c533567-3a40-4468-b503-f69dc35126c7">
<p local-id=3D"fe08f3dd-7794-4e24-b9b8-830037390f28"><strong>encryption key=
:</strong> d1c2e12cfeababc8b95daf6902e210b170992e68fd1c1f19565a40cf0099c6e2=
cb559b85d7c14ea05b4dca0a790656d003ccade9286827cffdf8e664fd271499</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"31ee84e7-8261-417d-9ae6-79bd60eeff77" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Endpoint">Endpoint</h3>
<p local-id=3D"081a3f77-00f2-4698-b29e-3a608ef674fe"><code>&lt;https://beta=
.tbibank.support/api/RegisterApplication</code>&gt;</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"0a6b59a5-98ce-4c0f-838e-661458a66751" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-RequestParameters.1">Request Parameters</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f4=
610699-fa50-43b4-8fca-d4a46bd631ba" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"eee6872e-2c23-42e7-b136-f98febc6429a">
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#ffc400" data-local-id=3D"4b6f14bf-559f-46fc-b=
f28-31f5a5bf5021" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1b8cb952-63c6-49bf-9349-e9d3b02e13c8"><strong>Parameter</str=
ong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#ffc400" data-local-id=3D"820b4da2-a49c-4d21-b=
8f0-bae123468df9" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"69c2846c-a7e1-4a10-b69f-b0e5b8a4d4af"><strong>Description</s=
trong></p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#ffc400" data-local-id=3D"51bae7ec-c51d-40c9-a=
a94-d044b5de3152" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b3e08115-783e-4385-ae95-f16fb10ae829"><strong>Type</strong><=
/p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#ffc400" data-local-id=3D"dc8f1f66-5be7-4d9a-9=
327-ae1f8b43422d" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3262e5ce-5d7d-425c-8867-dfeec5816ea9"><strong>Required</stro=
