D9;border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"panelContent" style=3D"background-color: #EAE6FF;">
<p local-id=3D"5762e370-dea5-419d-9c5e-d000a330339e"><strong>Note:</strong>=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"57664546-3b16-4868-8083-ac3e0eb74919">
<li local-id=3D"a1024766-9070-475e-a6d4-aa64c0a6ee97">
<p local-id=3D"b9814530-817b-4517-a847-37a5695bad9a"><code>imagelink</code>=
 is recommended because it enhances the page where the customer is redirect=
ed.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8838f5c-d64a-4324-b4fe-7fd198ee5242">
<p local-id=3D"95c7fa4f-500d-4789-9fec-b45700131eb6"><code>category</code> =
is mandatory to determine eligibility for promotional schemes.</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
