<p local-id=3D"ea0d0864-59b6-45de-8e54-9cf307486ba8">The body of the applic=
ation from the above example will have Promo scheme preselected and the app=
lication will have both <code>successRedirectURL</code> and <code>failRedir=
ectURL</code> defined.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
