<p local-id=3D"2d938830-240c-4d0a-b2f3-c510176c17b6"></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"59a0f6bd-2bb7-44c3-b5a0-65757b0215c2">
<li local-id=3D"b18139a7-0cf3-45b8-b639-d3a830863707">
<p local-id=3D"bedfe98d-29c1-4eaa-8af5-52a0a30a73ff"><strong>Missing Parame=
ters:</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "error": 203,
  "message": "Empty request /api/info203"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"30302362-6e94-4e4e-8e6c-49604a62d1de"><em>Indicates that the=
 request is missing required parameters.</em></p>
<ol start=3D"2" local-id=3D"99b54f46-a03c-4d69-9aa0-4ba7493fec75">
<li local-id=3D"43e229f4-ce5e-4293-b499-ba9c0e4ccd26">
<p local-id=3D"e55d1715-e9aa-438a-a349-ad0efff8f590"><strong>Total Basket A=
mount Outside Financing Ranges:</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "error": 210,
  "message": "Total basket amount (31000) is below or above financing limit=
s /api/info210"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"471adada-afd3-43e5-bf4e-458033959e9e"><em>Indicates that the=
 total basket amount exceeds the allowable financing limits.</em></p>
<ol start=3D"3" local-id=3D"905eefb3-41ca-4734-970c-353dd727ae07">
<li local-id=3D"c55d5b5e-cb31-4dc8-9a8d-ce3a0e5d2c98">
<p local-id=3D"9f76ddba-8a78-4d24-a3e6-ad789803c289"><strong>Incorrect Rese=
ller Code or Key Matching, or Incorrect Encryption:</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "error": 205,
  "message": "Access denied /api/info205"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"768d489e-fb06-4f4f-a34b-f52467f650ca"><em>Indicates that the=
re is an issue with the reseller code, key matching, or encryption used.</e=
m></p>
<ol start=3D"4" local-id=3D"7c2bd117-8caf-438a-9b0e-c69209ac29f5">
<li local-id=3D"f872c082-521f-4daa-8fb8-40ee3296d346">
<p local-id=3D"2f43eb4f-73ee-462d-b9a7-6e671cd25006"><strong>Incorrect Para=
meters:</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "error": 209,
  "message": "Missing mandatory parameters in the items list /api/info209"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"a6d4b6cb-0ff9-4ac4-b537-a1d2276b340d"><em>Indicates that the=
re are incorrect parameters provided in the request's items list.</em></p>
<p local-id=3D"4cd09d71-01cf-4e34-a498-808d31f7d023"></p>
<p local-id=3D"6eefb130-09aa-4e28-8722-f8aab83f31a3"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"684b3710-563b-48b9-b7c5-4e39bd09efb8" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-GetApplicationStatus">Get Applica=
tion Status</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"d3a6b86b-012d-4e4c-8337-cff3c88faa84" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-Overview.2">Overview</h3>
<p local-id=3D"01a8a7ac-c190-45e7-9985-ffa89766ce59"></p>
<p local-id=3D"fbf3b56b-bb64-46d1-8bd1-349f7b40a678">After successfully sen=
ding an application, the response will include an <code>order_id</code> and=
 <code>token</code>. You can use these, along with the <code>reseller_code<=
/code> and <code>reseller_key</code>, to request and track the application'=
s status and its movement through the assessment process. This API endpoint=
 exclusively supports the POST method.</p>
<div class=3D"panel" style=3D"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998D=
D9;border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"panelContent" style=3D"background-color: #EAE6FF;">
<p local-id=3D"a86326ac-1913-43a7-a988-7a6d68d9f960"><strong>This endpoint =
can be used to track status updates only if the </strong><code>statusURL</c=
ode><strong> variable in </strong><code>RegisterApplication</code><strong> =
is not provided (i.e., not included in the request)</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<ul local-id=3D"759d562d-586f-4e3c-ac0e-773310c64a34">
<li local-id=3D"4251e41e-bc91-4565-8338-edc86e6da30c">
<p local-id=3D"dbd75d66-1a2b-4434-aea2-3c7b08d77d15"><strong>Interface</str=
ong>: <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://beta.tbibank.support/api/G=
etApplicationStatus" rel=3D"nofollow">https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetA=
pplicationStatus</a></p></li>
</ul>
