<h3 local-id=3D"4a6973b9-ddc0-434a-a70f-c4d9ef46b9ec" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Examples.1">Examples</h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"3d91f534-062e-4003-a875-218e4e68dc72" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Input:">Input:</h4>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">curl --=
location '&lt;https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetApplicationStatus&gt;' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data '{
  "reseller_code": "TBI1",
  "reseller_key": "EX1",
  "order_id": 20,
  "token": "b5f80fc011c052231240e1cf267e9ebbbc55"
}'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h4 local-id=3D"cca605a8-c4aa-46cd-9b0d-e31b81fc205a" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Output:">Output:</h4>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "error": 0,
  "store_order_id": "230110114428803",
  "status": "Draft",
  "status_chain": [
    {
      "datetime": "30.03.2023 12:11:22",
      "status": "Draft"
    },
    {
      "datetime": "30.03.2023 12:15:22",
      "status": "InProgress"
    }
  ]
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"2398372b-6fee-436f-b4e2-ebfb169fd0dd">Here, <code>store_orde=
r_id</code> refers to the order ID on the merchant's side, which is sent in=
 the Register Application method.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"33c5cce9-e3cf-4175-9ac6-15a0783b5e54" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-GetApplicationData">Get Applicati=
on Data</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"4ae3df75-6e13-4af7-93f6-2ca319ec084a" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-Overview.3">Overview</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e9819176-b4d3-4873-88bb-81b2369a07de">After successfully sen=
ding an application, the response will include an <code>order_id</code> and=
 <code>token</code>. You can use these, along with the <code>reseller_code<=
/code> and <code>reseller_key</code>, to request and track the application'=
s data and some of its details like store_order_id (the id in the merchants=
 store), latest status, downpayment, installment and period of the loan app=
lication. This API endpoint exclusively supports the POST method.<br><br></=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"a793e843-17f7-434d-a982-c5b91ef70379">
<li local-id=3D"aa5b3848-fcea-48a0-a7c3-6310a2166bbf">
<p local-id=3D"e5bed8a1-6ac7-4a60-9c2e-55f69ec0b565"><strong>Interface</str=
ong>: <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://beta.tbibank.support/api/G=
etApplicationData" rel=3D"nofollow">https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetApp=
licationData</a></p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"246722e5-9743-4882-b251-81c21519a8db" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Parameters.1">Parameters</h3>
