<p local-id=3D"1595823c-9608-41d1-97cd-fbe9e9ddd1cf">String</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8a8d3bf0-e4df-4d94-8151-7073c62e167e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fc4a2757-0043-4f88-8584-22fd46c25e66">Yes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"184af195-214d-4f63-865d-0fa15285c109">
<td data-local-id=3D"c20a801b-3d4c-4941-b038-8e4a2f9840c6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"34ae0504-6f32-4693-b1e6-4a0ca9afb1be">order_id</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4eb51817-389e-4539-a823-ff0a333e4619" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2e3bd0c1-641f-48e7-a20b-854e88cdb13b">Order ID received with=
 Register Application method</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b038515a-f63d-4d2d-b8ac-dedc481a3678" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2ecf2479-03fd-4830-a744-27ccd174c2b8">Int</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"75966c2e-729a-4d45-800c-3cae0c68a3af" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7f0fe30a-7d2e-4425-bdaa-876d9b2162b9">Yes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1c7e3073-d9f2-4591-ade6-9a40bd59805c">
<td data-local-id=3D"4b17dae6-9ce9-4cd3-b22a-4840d4c90891" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d61dc1f2-2b24-4356-9fd4-8e5db0fa49b1">token</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a93584d3-1af5-4746-b061-00f8d368154e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7061ae0f-ec13-4ef5-abc5-c6b0f5e310c5">Token received with Re=
gister Application method</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8e515622-d7b4-4fcf-ad98-192957186b5e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b377171a-28d9-425d-9abd-08b63ab7e808">String</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"19c75e22-46c0-4fc0-9b49-e0a560f0268b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fbc2df73-fb82-409b-9dae-d3e0a77e209e">Yes</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"e648a780-f719-432a-a0ef-0bdb78838218" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Examples.2">Examples</h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"c78120ba-82fc-4bc4-909e-32cfceddd1c9" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Input:.1">Input:</h4>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">curl --=
location '&lt;https://beta.tbibank.support/api/GetApplicationData&gt;' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data '{
  "reseller_code": "TBI1",
  "reseller_key": "EX1",
  "order_id": 20,
  "token": "b5f80fc011c052231240e1cf267e9ebbbc55"
}'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h4 local-id=3D"7684d9d0-c350-403b-85f6-507dd1907380" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-Output:.1">Output:</h4>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
    "error": 0,
    "store_order_id": "2973",
    "status": "MP Sent",
    "downpayment": "1270.00",
    "installment": "146.07",
    "period": 12
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"0ef66db4-1b31-4521-a931-4bf6803462bb">Here, <code>store_orde=
r_id</code> refers to the order ID on the merchant's side, which is sent in=
 the Register Application method. <code>status</code> is the latest status =
of the application. <code>downpayment</code> is either <strong>NULL</strong=
> (if not downpayment is used or not eligible for the merchant) or a double=
 value - the amount of downpayment selected by the customer. <code>installm=
ent</code> is the amount of the monthly installment of the remaining amount=
. <code>period</code> is an integer and show the selected period of the app=
lication.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ee603ffc-9103-48e2-b28c-f62f9aae6aa5" style=3D"text-align: c=
enter;"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"2bbb4d85-9f30-48f6-8c3d-bcb7c7433c04" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-Ready-EmbeddedCalculator">Ready-E=
mbedded Calculator</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9ab16df4-a483-4cd9-96aa-8a363f9009f4"></p>
<p local-id=3D"f1715788-413b-4e66-8acd-4ded2065b9ac">Using the <code>resell=
er_code</code>, <code>reseller_key</code>, and the total basket amount, you=
 can call a dynamic URL to present available repayment schemes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"066bc529-e0dd-46ab-a8ed-ac54a1f34592">
<li local-id=3D"3b36080b-c17d-4c95-a0f1-acc8c5f478b2">
<p local-id=3D"f6da80f8-e4d4-48cf-9103-475d708624e9"><a class=3D"external-l=
ink" href=3D"https://beta.tbibank.support/application/calculcator/?code=3DT=
BI1&amp;key=3DEX1&amp;amount=3D1000" rel=3D"nofollow"><strong>Calculator wi=
th Total Amount</strong></a><strong> =E2=86=92 </strong>code=3D<strong>TBI1=
</strong>&amp;key=3D<strong>EX1</strong>&amp;amount=3D<strong>1000</strong>=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13796c73-0789-4e54-88e8-a32a19e0e59f">
<p local-id=3D"cf5dc0ea-12af-49d8-9aef-41192c8117a8"><a class=3D"external-l=
ink" href=3D"https://beta.tbibank.support/application/calculcator/?code=3DT=
BI1&amp;key=3DEX1&amp;amount=3D1000&amp;category=3D255" rel=3D"nofollow"><s=
trong>Calculator with Total Amount and Category</strong></a><strong> =E2=86=
=92 </strong>code=3DTBI1&amp;key=3DEX1&amp;amount=3D1000&amp;category=3D<st=
rong>255</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"28ed3850-9907-4a5d-b866-71bd29d58d9b">In the tbi system, add=
itional schemes can be added depending on the category ID. For example, the=
 second link above triggers two more schemes, which are only available for =
category ID 255. This category ID should also be sent in the item list cate=
gory field.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ae46a990-03ef-4433-a46f-5a62a9288696"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"728c08ad-f146-46c7-8d5c-15145c4dc604" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-ExpressBuyButtonIntegrationonProd=
uctPage">Express Buy Button Integration on Product Page</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c48ef12d-2014-4dbe-b57b-d9750ed43b23"></p>
<p local-id=3D"e84deba3-2fce-40a5-91e3-f338f49ae874">An express buy with tb=
i button can be implemented in product page using a callback if customer fi=
nishes the application in tbi redirected URL. To use this option the mercha=
nt need an endpoint which will receive a POST message with a body similar t=
o tbi RegisterApplication with encrypted data. This endpoint needs to retur=
n 'order_id' that is created in the merchant website.</p>
<p local-id=3D"01215808-b9f6-4bf8-83be-cd61aa8e8fe7">If the order_id has va=
lue 0 when registering the initial application tbi will send back the infor=
mation with customer details back to the mechant and will use the returned =
order_id to be visible in Merchant Portal.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"080ccfc2-9ed8-447c-afdc-738074ed38c8" id=3D"APIdocumentatio=
n-FusionPay-IntegrationProcessOverview:">Integration Process Overview:</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"a735d44d-2e4d-4f98-9fa9-647340389b9b">
<li local-id=3D"133afd1b-30db-4a19-94fa-3ec89e6f4732">
<p local-id=3D"3bf42505-3be2-46e8-9ff1-71381549970f"><strong>Merchant Initi=
alization</strong>: Send the application with missing data and <code>"order=
id": "0"</code> as follows:</p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "orderid": "0",
  "firstname": "",
  "lastname": "",
  "surname": "",
  "email": "",
  "phone": "",
  "deliveryaddress": {
    "country": "",
    "county": "",
    "city": "",
    "streetname": "",
    "streetno": "",
    "buildingno": "",
    "entranceno": "",
    "floorno": "",
    "apartmentno": "",
    "postalcode": ""
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Sport Elegant Pants",
      "description": "",
      "qty": "3",
      "price": "34.99",
      "sku": "3345",
      "category": "9",
      "imagelink": "&lt;https://tbi-uat.online/hat/hat.jpg&gt;"
    },
    {
      "name": "Blouse Raita",
      "description": "",
      "qty": "1",
      "price": "110.65",
      "sku": "5566",
      "category": "4",
      "imagelink": "&lt;https://tbi-uat.online/hat/hat.jpg&gt;"
    }
  ],
  "promo": true,
  "successRedirectURL": "&lt;https://testsuccess.com&gt;",
  "failRedirectURL": "&lt;https://testfail.com&gt;"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<ol start=3D"2" local-id=3D"fbffd406-0a13-46cc-8866-5915f9401452">
<li local-id=3D"72aa0267-bd39-4e40-8e69-90636757e447">
<p local-id=3D"1408e94c-4c1d-40fe-bc3f-842bcccddf13"><strong>TBI Response</=
strong>: TBI will respond with:</p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{=20
  "reseller_code": "TBI1",
  "reseller_key": "EX1",
  "data": "ENCRYPTED_BODY"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<ol start=3D"3" local-id=3D"598e317c-f95e-412b-9dc9-c2a48c1007fd">
<li local-id=3D"2317c56e-800b-4494-9deb-bebedbf1bcbd">
<p local-id=3D"7b30060c-b458-401e-a427-8e86b3ec1c9a"><strong>Decryption</st=
rong>: Decrypt the <code>data</code> field to obtain the following JSON for=
mat. Note that the <code>period</code> can represent either a period in mon=
ths or 'BNPL'. Also, the <code>sku</code> field is replaced with <code>code=
</code> in the items list:</p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "Dow",
  "surname": "",
  "email": "test@tbibank.bg",
  "phone": "0879123456",
  "deliveryaddress": {
    "country": "",
    "county": "",
    "city": "",
    "streetname": "",
    "streetno": "",
    "buildingno": "",
    "entranceno": "",
    "floorno": "",
    "apartmentno": "",
    "postalcode": ""
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Sport Elegant Pants",
      "description": "",
      "qty": "3",
      "price": "34.99",
      "code": "3345",
      "category": "111",
      "imagelink": "&lt;https://tbi-uat.online/hat/hat.jpg&gt;"
    },
    {
      "name": "Blouse Raita",
      "description": "",
      "qty": "1",
      "price": "110.65",
      "code": "5566",
      "category": "111",
      "imagelink": "&lt;https://tbi-uat.online/hat/hat.jpg&gt;"
    }
  ],
  "period": 34
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h1 local-id=3D"69da5eef-7741-440a-ab06-28958b2837b6" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-Addtocartfunctionality"><strong>A=
dd to cart functionality</strong></h1>
<p local-id=3D"b70bb3d3-231c-4b42-befb-95359d433030"></p>
<p local-id=3D"a0b25ad1-1ef7-43c3-a5ff-8c4e8a89a80c">On choosing a scheme a=
nd/or downpayment, our calculator=E2=80=99s JS will return a message via</p=
>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">targetW=
indow.postMessage(message, '*');</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"d6af0fe3-c070-421a-a1af-7c597641c5e6">The content of the mes=
sage will be a JSON in the following format as example</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{"schem=
e_id" : 477, "downpayment" : 150}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"6f2784d9-6384-4459-ba57-74640825523c">The Merchants website =
must catch this message and read it</p>
<p local-id=3D"b9e0f098-2aeb-48fd-b413-64f2b7f61209">Example code to includ=
e:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">const F=
PTBI_ORIGIN =3D 'https://beta.tbibank.support';
window.addEventListener('message', (e) =3D&gt; {
    if (e.origin =3D=3D=3D FPTBI_ORIGIN) {
        try {
            const jsonObject =3D JSON.parse(e.data);
            if (jsonObject.scheme_id !=3D=3D undefined || jsonObject.downpa=
yment !=3D=3D undefined) {
                // Merchants defatul logic for adding to cart, includiding =
the scheme_id and downpayment in some sort of session data
            }
            //if it's a success, then close the pop-up or return the produc=
t page with the default add to cart message
        } catch (error) {
          console.error('Invalid JSON string:', error);
        }
      }
    });</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"bdecd5bb-d96a-40c1-be30-54c84a899d38"></p>
<p local-id=3D"d2ed3083-8148-4d1e-85f9-27ae7a3ba509">We need the scheme_id =
and/or downpayment to be accessible in checkout. If they are - then include=
 them in the RegisterApplication request, just like that:</p>
<p local-id=3D"e4ca8d11-4a54-40ad-a774-e1f441443d7d"></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">$data_a=
rray =3D [
    "orderid" =3D&gt; "123",
    "firstname" =3D&gt; "=D0=A2=D0=B5=D1=81=D1=82",
    "lastname" =3D&gt; "=D0=A2=D0=B5=D1=81=D1=82=D0=BE=D0=B2",
    "surname" =3D&gt; "",
    "email" =3D&gt; "test@tbibank.bg",
    "phone" =3D&gt; "1231231231",
    "deliveryaddress" =3D&gt; [
        "country" =3D&gt; "Bulgaria",
        "county" =3D&gt; "",
        "city" =3D&gt; "=D0=A1=D0=BE=D1=84=D0=B8=D1=8F",
        "streetname" =3D&gt; "=D0=93=D0=9C =D0=94=D0=B8=D0=BC=D0=B8=D1=82=
=D1=80=D0=BE=D0=B2",
        "streetno" =3D&gt; "62",
        "buildingno" =3D&gt; "",
        "entranceno" =3D&gt; "",
        "floorno" =3D&gt; "321",
        "apartmentno" =3D&gt; "123",
        "postalcode" =3D&gt; ""
       =20
         ],
    "items" =3D&gt; [=09
        [
            "name" =3D&gt; "=D0=A1=D0=BF=D0=BE=D1=80=D1=82=D0=BD=D0=BE =D0=
=B5=D0=BB=D0=B5=D0=B3=D0=B0=D0=BD=D1=82=D0=B5=D0=BD =D0=BF=D0=B0=D0=BD=D1=
=82=D0=B0=D0=BB=D0=BE=D0=BD",
            "description" =3D&gt; "",
            "qty" =3D&gt; "3",
            "price" =3D&gt; "34.99",
            "sku" =3D&gt; "3345",
            "category" =3D&gt; "255",
            "imagelink" =3D&gt; "https://tbi-uat.online/hat/hat.jpg"
        ],
        [=09=09=09
            "name" =3D&gt; "=D0=91=D0=BB=D1=83=D0=B7=D0=B0 =D1=80=D0=B0=D0=
=B5=D1=82=D0=B0",
            "description" =3D&gt; "",
            "qty" =3D&gt; "1",
            "price" =3D&gt; "90.65",
            "sku" =3D&gt; "5566",
            "category" =3D&gt; "255",
            "imagelink" =3D&gt; "https://tbi-uat.online/hat/hat.jpg"
        ]
    ],
    "successRedirectURL" =3D&gt; "https://success.com",
    "failRedirectURL" =3D&gt; "https://fail.com",
   =20
    //add the values here
    "scheme_id" =3D&gt; 755,
=09"downpayment" =3D&gt; 155
];</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"bd3fddb0-779c-405f-9a5f-78edb3efdfe7"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"f9680779-0efb-489d-b5c4-1d7edfd3358b" style=3D"text-align: =
center;" id=3D"APIdocumentation-FusionPay-Examplefiles">Example files</h1>
<p local-id=3D"314c8295-958e-4b05-bfc7-d34ea321fd4b"></p>
<p local-id=3D"ad702c0e-1565-49ae-83a1-ee9020577d3f"><img height=3D"250" st=
yle=3D"margin: 2px; border: 1px solid #ddd; box-sizing: border-box; vertica=
l-align: text-bottom;" src=3D"b129f371cc5cf1a31799e7256fb3d14190b620b22aec6=
dcc12f1c8b188699bca" width=3D"250"> =E2=80=93 can be used as a reference to=
 get repayments schemes. registerApplication.php =E2=80=93 an example appli=
cation encryption and cURL request getStatusUpdate.php =E2=80=93 an example=
 cURL for status update</p>
<p local-id=3D"9a0d3d51-ee20-451f-8661-287164942360"><img height=3D"250" st=
yle=3D"margin: 2px; border: 1px solid #ddd; box-sizing: border-box; vertica=
l-align: text-bottom;" src=3D"630edba1211f7343aea14e8ec21eee06254a328fe5693=
2d890605463d73ac7e1" width=3D"250"> =E2=80=93 an encryption model file for =
encrypting sensitive data in the Register Application method.</p>
<p local-id=3D"32e2e0b1-4bf5-4cb5-9f72-fd41308a66f6"><em>For different prog=
ramming languages additional model files can be provided</em></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
